We are applying for the Available and Reusable badges. We believe our artifact deserves the badges for the following reasons:
1. The artifact is available on the public repository: https://github.com/kupl/NPEX_Artifacts
2. We provided the benchmarks used in the evaluation and scripts for conveniently reproducing the main results of the paper.
3. We provided detailed instructions to run the tool for an arbitrary Java NPE bug, so other researchers can easily evaluate our tool in their research.
